## Step 9: Proxy Config (Optional)

If CORS causes issues, add to `next.config.ts`:
```typescript
async rewrites() {
  return [
    {
      source: '/api/:path*',
      destination: 'http://localhost:8000/api/:path*',
    },
  ];
}
```

